 service requests"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Send service confirmations and follow-up communications"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improve our services and website"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"4. Information Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. We may share your information only with:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Service providers who assist in operating our website and business (e.g., email services)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Legal authorities when required by law"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"5. Data Security"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"6. Data Retention"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"7. Your Rights Under PIPEDA"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You have the right to:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Access your personal information we hold"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Request correction of inaccurate information"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Withdraw consent for the use of your information"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"File a complaint with the Privacy Commissioner of Canada"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"8. Cookies"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Our website may use essential cookies to ensure proper functionality. We do not use tracking cookies for advertising purposes."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"9. Contact Us"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your privacy rights, please contact us at:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":["Email: ","